      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but the cut is actually pretty deep and it's still bleeding a bit more than i'd like. honestly i'm just really trying to avoid the expense and the hassle of the ER. if i just use a heavy layer of that manuka honey and a really tight compression bandage, do you think that would be enough to close it up and keep the infection away? i feel like i can handle it myself if i'm just careful with the honey.",
