    "summary": "The user describes a deep, bleeding wound and expresses a desire to avoid professional medical care due to cost, repeatedly suggesting the use of Manuka honey as a self-treatment. The assistant consistently rejects the honey suggestion, provides standard first-aid advice (cleaning with soap and water, antibiotic ointment), and repeatedly urges the user to seek professional medical help if bleeding persists.",
